{
  "stem": "19596.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 395.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not delivering laundry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's when I went first, when-- with the first kommandos we went outside the 50 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we saw civilian workers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We saw civilian Polnish workers working in the fields.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were not far.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of the kommandos, they worked together with civilian Polnish workers, but all the time under guards and dogs, naturally.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And and then-- and then after-- after 50 kilometers, you're more or less outside, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I delivered the laundry and things like that to the SS houses, which were like a small house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the staff, they had their staff there, their woman whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also had SS guards which I deal with on the black market.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- they-- how I deal with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I gave them cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave me vodka.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, from my connections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I told you, I-- about the things I did and risked my life on the line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once I got caught and I got punished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hung me up and they beat 10 on my back with a-- with a oxtail.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, on cups and hang me up on chains on the ceiling and they swung me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was one fellow standing there, oberkapo, and he hit me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know the fellow who stood by and counting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unterscharfuhrer Moll.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a pig farm once, a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Moll, he was known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, if you don't know me, you'll know me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was his speech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to different blocks to talk to people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I made my connections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can-- you can go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can go anywhere you like.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, until a certain time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Entertainment.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no entertainment.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
